      • decryptor

        public static java.lang.String decryptor​(java.lang.String keyFile,
                                         java.lang.String messageFile)
                                  throws java.io.IOException
        Decryption method that handles opening the encrypted message file and returning the decrypted message. If the file can not be found, an error is returned.
        Parameters:
        keyFile - Key file location given by user
        messageFile - Message file location given by user
        Returns:
        String The decrypted message
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - Thrown if there are issues opening the given files
